metadata.name: Dream in Cappadocia #1
metadata.description:
Cappadoica, Turkey

I feel very lucky to have been born and raised in this magical place. When you are still child, you are so fascinated when you see these mysterious rocks. What are these? 
How was it formed? 
Who did it? 
Or did aliens live here? 
Who drew the shapes on it? 
and many more questions.

Now I am trying to convey this mysterious story to you through the eyes of my childhood.

Maybe we can find all these answers with together...
